    "The patterns shown in Chinese partnerships with the EU and the US have an exponential tendency.",
    "On the other hand, the pattern drawn by the EU and US collaborations has a more linear tendency, although it has increased its tendency positively in the last few years.",
    "The different patterns are repeated within the different topics, suggesting that the publication of journal articles is stable for the different regions, being more impacted by other factors than the popularity of the topics themselves.",
